These are Puzzles for 1x3 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-8-1::.
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: surfing, tennis, baseball
1. the person who's sport is surfing is on the far right##1
2. the person who's sport is surfing is not to the left of the person who's sport is tennis##8
3. the person who's sport is baseball is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is tennis##5

.:: Answer ::.
|         |       1       |    2    |    3     |
| Sport   | baseball | tennis | surfing |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-8-2::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: photography, magic-tricks, gardening
1. the person who's hobby is gardening is not to the left of the person who's hobby is photography##8
2. the person who's hobby is gardening is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1   |   2    |     3     |
| Hobby   | photography | gardening | magic-tricks |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-8-3::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, fanta, iced-tea
1. the person drinking fanta is on the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
2. the person drinking hot-chocolate is not to the right of the person drinking iced-tea##8

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |   2   |  3  |
| Beverage   | fanta | hot-chocolate | iced-tea |

 #################################

 
